HEADWORD: Muharram
<hw>Mu*har"ram</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr> }</mhw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Ar. <ets>muharram</ets>,
prop., sacred, forbidden, n., the first month of the Mohammedan lunar
